Q5. Print all available gateways in sorted order

manish@boss:~/Linux_practice_area$ netstat -rn
Kernel IP routing table
Destination     Gateway         Genmask         Flags   MSS Window  irtt Iface
0.0.0.0         192.168.1.1     0.0.0.0         UG        0 0          0 wlo1
192.168.1.0     0.0.0.0         255.255.255.0   U         0 0          0 wlo1
manish@boss:~/Linux_practice_area$ netstat -rn | tail -n +3 | awk '{print $2}' | uniq | sort
0.0.0.0
192.168.1.1


